name: Cross the Ages - Arkhante Booster Premium Pack
description:
The Arkhante Collection is the 1st NFT collection of Cross The Ages: TCG.
The Premium Collection gathers all the premium packs that can be opened in-game once the Early Access is live. Early Access started on October 12.

These packs grant multiple benefits to their owner such as early access to the game; 20 to 30 NFT cards; valuable mythical cards; access to the CTA Token Presale; and a secret NFT.

All details: https://www.crosstheages.com/arkhante-collection/
